{"version":1,"ops":[{"type":6,"author":{"id":"a015eff167a8f619e7336efedeccf87d5cc77758"},"timestamp":1622618551,"metadata":{"github-id":"MDE1OlVzZXJDb250ZW50RWRpdElzc3VlRWRpdDo1NDg4OTc5OTQ="},"target":"348bef8364a20429285e084c55ef76b0f8a0e2466bc73475b0c9ed9f64f8d821","message":"Hi,\nIn release version 0.12.4,(also in the latest commit 4c210bba) , dwg2SVG 0.12.4.4317\n\nThere is an infinite loop in functopn output_BLOCK_HEADER() in dwg2SVG.c\nOccur in the while loop at line 804 \n\n```c\n802\t  while (obj)\n803\t    {\n804\t      num += output_object (obj);\n805\t      obj = get_next_owned_entity (ref-\u003eobj, obj);\n806\t    }\n```\nRoot cause is in `dwg_next_entity`.\n\nIf function `dwg_ref_object_silent ` call `return dwg_ref_object_silent (obj-\u003eparent, next);` \n\nand then  `obj = bj-\u003etio.entity-\u003enext_entity-\u003eobj`, the loop happened\n\n\n\n```c\n1092\t    {\n1093\t      if (!obj-\u003etio.entity) // decoding error\n1094\t        goto next_obj;\n1095\t      next = obj-\u003etio.entity-\u003enext_entity;\n1096\t      if (next \u0026\u0026 next-\u003eabsolute_ref)\n1097\t        return dwg_ref_object_silent (obj-\u003eparent, next);\n1098\t      else\n1099\t        goto next_obj;\n1100\t    }\n\n$57 = (const Dwg_Object * restrict) 0x7fffeeb3ea88\ngefÔŞñ  p obj-\u003etio.entity\n$58 = (Dwg_Object_Entity *) 0x6120000031c0\ngefÔŞñ  p obj-\u003etio.entity-\u003enext_entity\n$59 = (BITCODE_H) 0x6040000073d0\ngefÔŞñ  p obj-\u003etio.entity-\u003enext_entity-\u003eobj\n$60 = (struct _dwg_object *) 0x7fffeeb3ea88\n```\n\n**reproduce**\n\n./configure --enable-release\nmake\n./bin/dwg2SVG [poc]\n[zipped poc](https://github.com/LibreDWG/libredwg/files/6582616/infinite_loop_dwg_next_entity.zip)","files":null},{"type":6,"author":{"id":"a015eff167a8f619e7336efedeccf87d5cc77758"},"timestamp":1622618685,"metadata":{"github-id":"MDE1OlVzZXJDb250ZW50RWRpdElzc3VlRWRpdDo1NDg4OTk1MTQ="},"target":"348bef8364a20429285e084c55ef76b0f8a0e2466bc73475b0c9ed9f64f8d821","message":"Hi,\nIn release version 0.12.4,(also in the latest commit 4c210bba) , dwg2SVG 0.12.4.4317\n\nThere is an infinite loop in functopn output_BLOCK_HEADER() in dwg2SVG.c\nOccur in the while loop at line 804 \n\n```c\n//dwg2SVG.c\n802\t  while (obj)\n803\t    {\n804\t      num += output_object (obj);\n805\t      obj = get_next_owned_entity (ref-\u003eobj, obj);\n806\t    }\n```\nRoot cause is in `dwg_next_entity`.\n\nIf function `dwg_ref_object_silent ` call `return dwg_ref_object_silent (obj-\u003eparent, next);` \n\nand then  `obj = bj-\u003etio.entity-\u003enext_entity-\u003eobj`, the loop happened\n\n\n```c \n//dwg.c\n1803 dwg_next_entity (const Dwg_Object *restrict obj)\n1092\t    {\n1093\t      if (!obj-\u003etio.entity) // decoding error\n1094\t        goto next_obj;\n1095\t      next = obj-\u003etio.entity-\u003enext_entity;\n1096\t      if (next \u0026\u0026 next-\u003eabsolute_ref)\n1097\t        return dwg_ref_object_silent (obj-\u003eparent, next);\n1098\t      else\n1099\t        goto next_obj;\n1100\t    }\n\n$57 = (const Dwg_Object * restrict) 0x7fffeeb3ea88\ngefÔŞñ  p obj-\u003etio.entity\n$58 = (Dwg_Object_Entity *) 0x6120000031c0\ngefÔŞñ  p obj-\u003etio.entity-\u003enext_entity\n$59 = (BITCODE_H) 0x6040000073d0\ngefÔŞñ  p obj-\u003etio.entity-\u003enext_entity-\u003eobj\n$60 = (struct _dwg_object *) 0x7fffeeb3ea88\n```\n\n**reproduce**\n\n./configure --enable-release\nmake\n./bin/dwg2SVG [poc]\n[zipped poc](https://github.com/LibreDWG/libredwg/files/6582616/infinite_loop_dwg_next_entity.zip)","files":null},{"type":5,"author":{"id":"4044e69633a068fb3769d4cf7ce5f6bebf15d0f1"},"timestamp":1622624796,"metadata":{"github-id":"MDEyOkxhYmVsZWRFdmVudDQ4MzAzMjc4OTk="},"added":["blocking"],"removed":[]},{"type":5,"author":{"id":"4044e69633a068fb3769d4cf7ce5f6bebf15d0f1"},"timestamp":1622624796,"metadata":{"github-id":"MDEyOkxhYmVsZWRFdmVudDQ4MzAzMjc5MDI="},"added":["bug"],"removed":[]}]}